WEBVTT

00:00:00.858 --> 00:00:04.635
I want to tell you a story about stories.

00:00:05.510 --> 00:00:09.033
And I want to tell you this story
because I think we need to remember

00:00:09.057 --> 00:00:11.249
that sometimes the stories
we tell each other

00:00:11.273 --> 00:00:15.686
are more than just tales
or entertainment or narratives.

00:00:16.482 --> 00:00:18.188
They're also vehicles

00:00:18.212 --> 00:00:22.081
for sowing inspiration
and ideas across our societies

00:00:22.105 --> 00:00:23.608
and across time.

00:00:24.800 --> 00:00:26.292
The story I'm about to tell you

00:00:26.316 --> 00:00:29.381
is about how one of the most advanced
technological achievements

00:00:29.405 --> 00:00:30.557
of the modern era